_sText:
This map took forever to make, bug after bug, I finally finished it. Thanks to all that helped with ideas!

This map includes:

A rap around trampoline
A pool
A giant diving board
A maze
A player controlled helicopter
A secret room
A gun toss
Costumes
A booster

ALL IN ONE!

Only one team you can join to prevent killing of any kind: COUNTER TERRORISTS.

Let me know what you think. If you put it on your server please tell!

Thanks to Xeno for helping me with this map the most.
